data.description: Lovely home with lots of attention to detail. Spacious entry into open concept living, dining and kitchen, with vaulted ceilings filled with plenty of natural light. Beautiful LVP flooring throughout common area. Kitchen is complete with custom cabinets, quartz counters and breakfast bar. Large dining area leads out through sliding glass doors to easy entertaining covered deck and patio. 4-bedrooms and 2.5 baths allow accommodations for everyone. Large Master bedroom with private ensuite. Double sink vanity with quartz counters and dual shower heads. Large walk-in closet. Plenty of room in this fully fenced backyard that adds a feeling of privacy. 2 car garage. Room for large, detached shop. Easy access neighborhood of newer homes, walking distance to park, near shopping, restaurants, Lake Pend Oreille, and Schweitzer Mt. Resort.  Assumable VA loan at approx 2.8% interest. Buyer will have to qualify.
